data.description: Gorgeous four bedroom home with really large bedrooms. This home features a beautiful dining room open to the living area perfect to entertain during the holidays. The kitchen has ample counterspace and plenty of cabinets as well as a breakfast area and a walk in Pantry. The master bedroom features high ceilings and the master bath has tile shower and separate soaking tub. Always wanted your own walk in closet ? You are in luck this one has two master closets. Really great home with fenced backyard and plenty of room for cooking out on the back patio. It is a neighborhood that has no HOA and the elementary school is within walking distance. Easy access to 195 for a smooth drive into Austin. Make an appointment today !
